com.googlecode.mobilityrpc.controller.impl

Interface MobilityControllerInternal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Destroyable, IncomingMessageHandler, MobilityController, OutgoingMessageHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MobilityControllerImpl

    public interface MobilityControllerInternal
extends MobilityController, IncomingMessageHandler, OutgoingMessageHandler
    A combination of several internal interfaces implemented by the mobility controller, most of which are not part of the public API. Only MobilityController is part of the public API.
    Author:
    Niall Gallagher
